dc_title_s: Map of a portion of the Miami River Basin at the Loramie and Mosquito Creek Area showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Loramie and Mosquito Creek Area and quality of underground water.|Scale bar lower left corner of map.|"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"|Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
